# YPA README screenshots — drop PNGs here with these exact names.
# They are linked from README.md by relative path and ride along into
# the public snapshot automatically: publish-org.ps1 builds from the
# committed HEAD tree and strips only the private pets + itself.
# COMMIT the images before publishing — the publisher ignores the
# working tree, so anything uncommitted will not ship.
#
#   hero.png             chat + node editor, mid-record   (~900px wide)
#   full.png             Full layout
#   code.png             Code view (VSCode-style workspace)
#   workflow.png         Workflow node editor
#   split.png            Split view (graph + chat)
#   messenger.png        Messenger layout
#   zen.png              Zen layout
#   theme-atelier.png    Atelier design
#   theme-console.png    Console design
#   theme-patchbay.png   Patchbay design
#   color-smoke-{bright,dark}.png    grayscale pair
#   color-prism-{bright,dark}.png    colorful pair
#   color-minimal-{bright,dark}.png  minimal pair
#   color-void-{bright,dark}.png     stark / very-dark pair
#   color-ocean-{bright,dark}.png    cool pair
#   color-sunset-{bright,dark}.png   warm pair
#   pet.png              the pet companion (~230px wide is plenty)
